  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidSequenceException
    InvalidSequenceException class - The password cannot contain more than two of the same character in sequence of a user-inputed password.
    LengthException
    LengthException class - The user-inputed password must be at least 6 characters long.
    NoDigitException
    NoDigitException class - The user-inputed password must contain at least a single digit
    NoLowerAlphaException
    NoLowerAlphaException class - The user-inputed password must contain at least one lowercase alphabetic based character.
    NoSpecialCharacterException
    NoSpecialCharacterException class - The user-inputed password must contain one special character or more.
    NoUpperAlphaException
    NoUpperAlphaException class - The user-inputed password must contain one or more uppercase alphabetic characters.
    UnmatchedException
    UnmatchedException class - The user-inputed password does not match to the re-typed version.
    WeakPasswordException
    WeakPasswordException class - The user-inputed password is OK but it is weak, because the password is less than 10 characters.
